Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, everybody on the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of the New Fish-Man \NPirates from the Fish-Man District,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:04:03.39,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Kingdom in Shock! \NAn Order to Execute Neptune Issued!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't step on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Queen Otohime would forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I refuse, they'll kill \Nme! I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you pass! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring! Surprisingly,\N they're all just stepping on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime was not that \Nwell-respected after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daruma-san, Captain Hordy is on the air now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So he is the one who is behind all of this!\N--He made us step on the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't he the one who killed \Nthe assassin of Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, his name is Hordy Jones!\N I'm sure it was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he a soldier of Neptune's army?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:16.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I want \Nto tell all citizens of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:20.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}SEA FOREST
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Ryugu Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will soon be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will be rebuilt under a new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:42.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}CORAL HILL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is?! Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is he broadcasting from?\N--What happened to the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Straw Hats occupied \Nthe palace - what happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Fish-Man Island over which I will \Nrule is going to be strict in discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who hope for \Nfriendly relations with humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get packing and leave this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are weak and they \Ndon't know their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't deserve any help\N from us strong Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, we will have new residents\N from the Fish-Man District soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hate humans and hope to \Nchange this island like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the same camp as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:32.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What? New residents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.45,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}WATERWHEEL TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:41.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All those outlaws will come and live with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you all witnessed how your\N beloved Queen Otohime died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so selfless and tried so hard to \Nbuild a bridge between Fish-Men and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who killed her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trust them and meet halfway\Nin friendship, they'll disappoint you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duped by the Neptune family, you are \Nall heading down the path of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their high-sounding \Ndream is just unfeasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie that will lead you to perdition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Knight Neptune \Ngot old like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no future for the Fish-Man \NIsland if the old guard remains in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately the King \Nwas captured because of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Nami-san. \NIt's all that Moss Head's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you people do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But, Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers of Neptune's army attacked\N Nami-chin and the others first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune's army?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the old Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours from now, at Conchcorde Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cut this \Nincompetent King's head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Pirate Era began...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when they executed a human -\NGold Roger, the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That era saw humans grow \Nto persecute Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, by executing Neptune,\N I'll start the Great Fish-Man Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where Fish-Men will dominate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you may know by now, I'm at the Ryugu Palace\N as I speak. And we found something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the letter from the Celestial Dragons\N that Queen Otohime got 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the risk of her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy that letter, it's over.\N You won't get another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this big box,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are signatures from \Nthe majority of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many fools who\N want to befriend humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who have signed your \Nname would oppose my new kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a list of traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more stepping on her picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be easy to pretend \Nyou don't mind stepping on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these signatures will tell\N who is my enemy and who is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take care of those enemies one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togare from Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I... I'm not... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Gotan from Waterwheel Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luca from Mermaid Cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia from Fishverly Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meverly from the Coral Apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you hurt my folk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, enough for now. \NWe don't have time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are somewhere on \Nthe island watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people shattered Arlong's dream \N- he was a symbol of Fish-Men's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What fools...\N--I can't believe they got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh? Oh? Oh? Oh?\N--Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's this noise?\N--It's like a roar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's water!\N--It's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That room will be filled with water by \Nthe time we finish executing the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly creatures can't\N survive that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy with a 400\N million berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your people's heads will serve perfectly\N as a lesson to humans above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start cleaning \Nup the old Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bury the embarrassing past and shift\N the helm towards the great future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man Island will win \Nback its pride in three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let them do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, issue an order to Daruma \Nand the others to assemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna get busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make your execution a big show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that all citizens of the \NFish-Man Island will be afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be so selfish? \NYou can't govern a country like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All kings are selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a selfish king to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Otohime's dream made me sick \Never since I was a soldier in your army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the leader changes, \Na country will change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the "law" from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The water level keeps rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san, I just got dry. \NI don't wanna soak in sea water again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Zoro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...untie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it! I feel my psychic power!\NChains, come off! Chains, come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chains, come off! Come \Noff, chains! Come off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I don't have any psychic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The look on those Fish-Men's\N faces when I moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't moving. Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should stay dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with \Nthese skeletal remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they even get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they flowed in with the water when \NCaptain Hordy broke the wall of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pull them up onto the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook can free us later if he \Nkeeps pretending to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was adrift at sea. I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been dead for 50 years or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm a dead skeleton--Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't stop laughing \Njust thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got caught because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! They're gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least Nami and the others got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can bring Luffy and the others here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if they don't come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I hope Nami hasn't been \Neaten by a deep-sea fish."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds exactly like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is different from any of \NPoneglyphs than I've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a letter... A letter of apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you apologizing to? And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Joy Boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I'm worth 400 million!\N When did they raise it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, they want to fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The War of the Best at Marineford\N made you infamous instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it goes over 300 million,\N it's not easily increased again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if somebody wants \Nto fight me, I'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait, Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama! Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei-sama! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, Princess-sama,\N both of you have to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I don't think you should go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Hordy is most afraid of \Nin the Ryugu Kingdom now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Princess Shirahoshi's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he reshapes the Fish-Man \NIsland exactly the way he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once she controls the Sea Kings \Nto attack the island, it'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the King hostage\N to use him as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what they're really going\N for is Shirahoshi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy is not planning to capture \Nher and get control of her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He prefers her power didn't exist at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he teamed up with Decken\N who is capable of killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy wants to get rid of everything\N that could stand in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rushing to the plaza is just what \NHordy wants Princess-sama to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been told about my power but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have never communicated\N with the Sea Kings-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I really\N have that kind of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I'm sure that \NHordy will try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we shouldn't let Hordy know \Nthat you can't control the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that he is afraid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all? Then I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Take me to the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, take care of Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait," Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people shouldn't fight Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two shouldn't say that! \NIt makes things more complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You humans shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The surviving Fish-Men \Nwill hate humans again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! They have my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I got to do something about Hordy \Nbefore my friends get into real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going.\N--You're impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't let my guard down \Njust because we fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot that \Nyou're that man's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to \Nlisten to me, I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:23:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Jinbei's emotional \Nbattle has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy faces the overwhelming force \Nof Jimbei's Fish-Man Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their duel is interrupted, \Nand takes an unexpected turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Rift Opens Up!\NLuffy vs. Jimbei!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
